ang he presented on the dynamics between energy security and climate change in china in addition pesd working paper 88 was featured in the conference and included in esi bulletin on energy trends and development related links cover real drivers of carbon capture and storage in china and implications for climate policy richard k morse varun rai gang he program on energy and sustainable development working paper 88 2009 html+ pdf+ esi bulletin the real drivers of carbon capture and storage in china richard k morse varun rai gang he esi bulletin vol 3 2010 pdf+ html+ energy studies institute http www esi nus edu sg portal search news everything news of interest pesd researcher gang he selected as aspen environment forum scholar may 27 2011 news trading carbon magazine features a new article by pesd researchers richard morse and gang he june 9 2010 news more efforts are needed to promote widespread ccs adoption says pesd researcher gang he in the news china dialogue on march 1 2010 support map & directions contact rss+ rss xml feeds freeman spogli institute for international studies encina hall 616 serra st stanford ca 94305 6055 tel 650 724 1714 fax 650 725 2592 mail code 6055
